      "content": "I see. So basically, the debate is between people who are worried about science fiction scenarios and people who want to focus on real-world progress. If you had to weigh them, is the risk of \"speculative doom\" actually a valid foundation for building law, or is it just an unproven theory that might end up hurting society more than it helps?",
